      "webTitle": "Carwyn Jones agrees to inquiry in Carl Sargeant case",
      "webUrl": "https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/nov/10/pressure-grows-welsh-first-minister-carwyn-jones-carl-sargeant-inquiry",
